# Genesis generator output (contains private keys — never commit).
# `genesis_testnet.json` is excluded when produced in the working
# directory by `generate_testnet_genesis`, but the *bundled template*
# under `savitri-core/src/core/genesis/` only contains dummy 0x000…001
# addresses and is part of the source — exempt it explicitly so
# `include_str!` resolves at build time.
genesis_testnet.json
